<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق وع:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَاعُ)</span> الْمُسْتَوِي مِنَ الْأَرْضِ، وَالْجَمْعُ <span class="c2">(أَقْوُعٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَقْوَاعٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(قِيعَانٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الْقِيعَةُ)</span> مِثْلُ الْقَاعِ.<span class="c5"> وَبَعْضُهُمْ يَقُولُ:</span> هُوَ جَمْعٌ. وَ <span class="c2">(قَاعَةُ)</span> الدَّارِ سَاحَتُهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>